OL,3,CFirst person in UK receives heart
OL,4,Cvalve replacement at John Radcliffe
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FSurgeons in have carried out the first
OL,8,Fprocedure of its kind in the UK on a
OL,9,Fpatient with severe heart valve
OL,10,Fdisease.
OL,12,FBefore the groundbreaking treatment at
OL,13,F, 79 year-old Rosalind Walsh had
OL,14,Fdebilitating symptoms including
OL,15,Fbreathlessness.
OL,17,F"I couldn't walk two steps or even get
OL,18,Fup from a chair without feeling
OL,19,Fbreathless," said Rosalind.
