OL,7,F"I went from being able to handle all
OL,8,Fmy housework and drive my car, to
OL,9,Fbeing able to do nothing.
OL,11,FAt one point her illness got so
OL,12,Fsevere, she spent almost a month in
OL,13,FA&E. It was here where she was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with a leaking heart valve,
OL,15,For Tricupsid Regurgitation. They
OL,16,Fdrained 15kg of water from her body.
OL,18,FWhat is Tricuspid Regurgitation?
