OL,7,FValve repairs had been possible for
OL,8,Fyears but valve replacement was only
OL,9,Fpossible with open heart surgery. But
OL,10,Ffollowing years of clinical trials,
OL,11,Fthe team at Oxford Heart Centre, based
OL,12,Fat the John Radcliffe Hospital, were
OL,13,Fable to treat patients with the
OL,14,Fcondition.
