OL,7,FTranscatheter Tricuspid Valve
OL,8,FReplacement (TTVR) procedures involve
OL,9,Freplacing the leaky valve with a new
OL,10,Fvalve. It is delivered through a leg
OL,11,Fvein, under a light anaesthetic,
OL,12,Favoiding the need for open heart
OL,13,Fsurgery.
OL,15,FPatients do not need to spend time on
OL,16,Fan intensive care unit and should be
OL,17,Fable to leave hospital within a couple
OL,18,Fof days.
