OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FDr Sam Dawkins, an Interventional
OL,8,FCardiologist at John Radcliffe,
OL,9,Fcarried out the procedures. He says
OL,10,Fits main benefit is how it avoids the
OL,11,Fneed for long spells in intensive care.
OL,13,F"Oxford is the first centre in the
OL,14,Fworld to use the device outside
OL,15,Fclinical trials, which is an amazing
OL,16,Fthing for the team here and for the
OL,17,FNHS as a whole," said Dawkins.
OL,19,FTricupsid Regurgitation is "so
OL,20,Fdebilitating and limiting to
OL,21,Fpatients", according to Dr Dawkins.
