OL,7,F"Now we have this new technologies
OL,8,Favailable we've seen these amazing
OL,9,Ftransformations. All the patients
OL,10,Fwe've treated since have a similar
OL,11,Fresponse. They have a procedure that's
OL,12,Flow risk, quick recovery and they come
OL,13,Finto clinic after procedure completely
OL,14,Ftransformed."
OL,16,FRosalind said her life has changed
OL,17,Fdramatically since she had the
OL,18,Fprocedure in December 2023, saying the
OL,19,Fstaff at the John Radcliffe made her
OL,20,Ffeel "like a celebrity" with a cupcake
OL,21,Fsaying 'UK first' on it.
