OL,7,F"I don't want to sound too dramatic,
OL,8,Fbut it feels as if though a miracle
OL,9,Fhas happened to me," believes
OL,10,FRosalind. "I feel so much better than
OL,11,Fbefore I had it done!"
OL,13,FShe's now able to drive her car again
OL,14,Fand is focusing on writing a book.
OL,15,FMedics hope that more people all over
OL,16,Fthe country with the condition can
OL,17,Fbegin to lead a normal life.
